methodology.UserFees: Users pay a trading fee from 0.04% to 0.4% on each swap (as of July 2022, the fee on all pools was 0.04%)
methodology.Revenue: A 50% of the trading fee is collected by veCRV holders
methodology.HoldersRevenue: A 50% of the trading fee is collected by the users who have vote locked their CRV
methodology.SupplySideRevenue: A 50% of all trading fees are distributed among liquidity providers
